<h2 class="pdoc-module-header" id="Channel">
<a class="pdoc-member-name" href="https://github.com/pulumi/pulumi-aws/blob/b468ea2e053d377b0786dfb645f5ee37a4f8a0e2/sdk/nodejs/mediapackage/channel.ts#L24">class <b>Channel</b></a>
</h2>
<div class="pdoc-module-contents">
<pre class="highlight"><span class='kd'>extends</span> <a href='/docs/reference/pkg/nodejs/pulumi/pulumi/#CustomResource'>CustomResource</a></pre>
{{% md %}}

Provides an AWS Elemental MediaPackage Channel.

## Example Usage

```typescript
import * as pulumi from "@pulumi/pulumi";
import * as aws from "@pulumi/aws";

const kittens = new aws.mediapackage.Channel("kittens", {
    channelId: "kitten-channel",
    description: "A channel dedicated to amusing videos of kittens.",
});
```

> This content is derived from https://github.com/terraform-providers/terraform-provider-aws/blob/master/website/docs/r/media_package_channel.html.markdown.
